    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i really dont want to call a doctor over a glass of juice, it seems overreacting lol. if i just drink it once in a while, like maybe once every couple days, wouldn't my body just process it okay? can't I just take the pill a few hours later to be safe?",
